              <span><i class="fas fa-gamepad"></i> 6 Matches</span>
              <span class="maps"><i class="fas fa-map"></i> Maps: Erangel, Miramar, Rondo, Miramar, Rondo, Erangel</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="section-title">Map Rotation</h2>
      <div class="map-grid">
        <div class="map-card">
          <img src="/data/img/erangle.jpg" alt="Erangel" loading="lazy">
          <div class="map-name">Erangel</div>
        </div>
        <div class="map-card">
          <img src="/data/img/miramar.jpg" alt="Miramar" loading="lazy">
          <div class="map-name">Miramar</div>
        </div>
        <div class="map-card">
          <img src="/data/img/rondo.jpg" alt="Rondo" loading="lazy">
          <div class="map-name">Rondo</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="section-title">Prize Pool & Rewards</h2>
      <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: -10px; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">PRIZE POOL: ‚Çπ13,000</p>
      <div class="reward-grid" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <div class="reward-card gold">
          <span class="reward-icon">ü•á</span>
          <div class="reward-rank">Winner</div>
          <div class="reward-amount">‚Çπ7,200</div>
          <div class="reward-extra">+ Trophy & Certificate</div>
        </div>
        <div class="reward-card silver">
          <span class="reward-icon">ü•à</span>
          <div class="reward-rank">Runner Up</div>
          <div class="reward-amount">‚Çπ2,500</div>
          <div class="reward-extra">+ Trophy & Certificate</div>
        </div>
        <div class="reward-card bronze">
          <span class="reward-icon">ü•â</span>
          <div class="reward-rank">3rd Place</div>
          <div class="reward-amount">‚Çπ1,500</div>
          <div class="reward-extra">+ Certificate</div>
        </div>
        <div class="reward-card mvp">
          <span class="reward-icon">üéñ</span>
          <div class="reward-rank">MVP</div>
          <div class="reward-amount">‚Çπ500</div>
          <div class="reward-extra">Individual Performance Award</div>
        </div>
        <div class="reward-card">
          <span class="reward-icon">üèÖ</span>
          <div class="reward-rank">4th-16th</div>
          <div class="reward-amount">‚Çπ100</div>
          <div class="reward-extra">With Certificates</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="section-title" id="rules">Tournament Rules</h2>
      <div class="rules-container">
        <div class="rules-grid">
          <div class="rule-card highlight-rule">
            <h4>üìπ Mandatory POV Recording</h4>
            <p>Each team MUST have at least <strong>one player</strong> recording continuous POV (with team audio) for every match. Failure to provide POV when requested may result in disqualification.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rule-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Team Format</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Squad (4 Primary + 1 Sub)</li>
              <li>64 Total Squads in 4 Groups (A, B, C, D)</li>
              <li>Stage 1: 4 groups √ó 16 teams each</li>
              <li>Stage 2: 4 groups √ó 8 teams each</li>
              <li>Grand Finals: Top 16 teams</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="rule-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i> Scoring System</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>1st Place: 10 pts | 2nd: 6 pts</li>
              <li>3rd: 5 pts | 4th: 4 pts</li>
              <li>5th: 3 pts | 6th: 2 pts</li>
              <li>7th: 1 pt | 8th-16th: 0 pts</li>
              <li>Kill Point: 1 per elim</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="rule-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> Game Settings</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Classic TPP Mode</li>
              <li>Mobile / Tab / iPad (No Emulators)</li>
              <li>Map Rotation: Erangel, Miramar, Rondo</li>
              <li>Registrations: Closed</li>
              <li>Online Qualifiers & LAN Finals</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="rule-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-gavel"></i> Fair Play</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>No Cheats/GFX Tools</li>
              <li>No Account Sharing</li>
              <li>Must use Registered UID/IGN</li>
              <li>Stream Delay: Min 3-5 mins</li>
              <li>Admins' Decision is Final</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
